  "response": "It's subjective to label any character in \"Friends\" as the \"most stupid,\" as each character has their quirks and strengths. However, Joey Tribbiani is often portrayed as the least intelligent among the group. His comedic charm, cluelessness, and humorous one-liners often highlight his naivety and lack of common sense. Despite this, Joey is beloved for his loyalty and his good-hearted nature. Each character adds to the show's dynamic in their own way, and many fans appreciate Joey's character for the laughs he brings.",
